lock theory presents some non trivial dynamics that can be\nassociated with a resolution of spatial infinity, and the $v$-clock theory does\nnot show significant deviations from the classical theory. In the last part, we\nexpand our analysis in order to include another quantisation method: path\nintegral quantisation, and finally, we conclude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2022 19:44:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-18"}
