 method can hide a color\nimage of the same size in another color image, which can be inferred that the\nrelative capacity of the proposed method is 8 bits per pixel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2022 08:39:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-18"}
