nclude, amongst others, orbit maintenance around\nMars as well as refuelling and space tug missions. The results show that the\nABEP system is not only able to compensate drag for orbit maintenance but also\ncapable of performing orbital maneuvers and collect propellant for applications\nsuch as Space Tug and Refuelling. Thus, showing a multitude of different future\nmission applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2022 12:35:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 09:48:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-22"}
